</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF6F6AD0FA9593C21827BED7" pageId="148" pageNumber="909" type="activity">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF6F6AD0FA9593C21827BED7" blockId="148.[1385,2592,1125,1666]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF6F6AD0FA9593C21856BE8E" bold="true" box="[1385,1622,1435,1468]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The type may have been hibernating in or near the house where it was captured.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
