</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF6F6AD0FA97904B141CBD68" pageId="148" pageNumber="909" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF6F6AD0FA97904B141CBD68" blockId="148.[1385,2592,1125,1666]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF6F6AD0FA97904B18C8BD01" bold="true" box="[1387,1736,1554,1587]" pageId="148" pageNumber="909">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The only known specimen was collected about a century ago. Virtually nothing is known aboutit.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
